text: Honestly one of the best Horror games I've played. It's not really that scary, but it really made me feel like someone was stepping on my grave. It has really good atmosphere and a fantastic story. I honestly couldn't praise it more. Only down side is that It's pretty short. Clocking in at around 5 hours (First run), But it's free for ps+ users so why not give it a try.

author: Jirt

text:
@Mdude360
It's more about the atmosphere and fear and intimidation play a big part in that. There are times you will be scared, but most of the game is more or less depressing and disturbing. The game for whatever reason get's under my skin. It really does set a mood. Highly recommend checking it out even if you're not into it's genre. Just make sure it's on a sale because it is pretty cheap.
